ai-patthana9.14:0.2_0: (This should be expanded as in MN 4.)
ai-patthana9.14:0.3_0: he struck by borrowed goods, thorns, and skilled in means.
ai-patthana9.14:3.1_1: One is not skilled in corruptions.
ai-patthana9.14:5.1_0: That is the cause, based on the five reasons, relying on letting go, five lower fetters are not rid of greed, hate, and delusion.
ai-patthana9.14:6.1_0: nor is there skilled in corruptions.
ai-patthana9.14:6.1_1: nor is there a pretext to settlement?
ai-patthana9.14:7.1_0: for the sake of letting go, two results, together with the five results of deeds ...
ai-patthana9.14:8.1_0: nor to grasp at a root, nor is held on the side of the unskillful.
ai-patthana9.14:8.1_1: nor do they remain in the teaching.
ai-patthana9.14:10.1_0: nor to grasp at a root, nor is there a stone that gives rise to unskillful qualities.
ai-patthana9.14:10.1_1: nor are they corrupted by corruptions,
ai-patthana9.14:10.1_2: There is no pretext to confuse, combin, or skilled in loss.
ai-patthana9.14:10.1_3: Infinitely, and not committed to wakefulness. ...
ai-patthana9.14:11.1_1: But when he is committed to the practice of corrupting, nor is there to be dangers.
